    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order containing 18 species in one family of fruit-eating large birds with brilliant purple, green, and crimson plumage and a prominent crest.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
